    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――買い出しの翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 966.6666825,
          "startTime": 0.9666666825
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5700,
          "startTime": 5.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣に呼ばれて来たけど……なんの用事なんだ？",
      "startTime": 1.8000000159,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11833.333746499999,
          "startTime": 13.6333337624
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13100.0004132,
          "startTime": 14.9000004291
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12266.6670799,
          "startTime": 14.0666670958
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！　{user}さん来たよー！\nじゃあ、せーの！　おっつかれさま～～！",
      "startTime": 10.8666670958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと……誰かの誕生日だったか？\n一応、誕生日は全員分、覚えてたはずなんだが……",
      "startTime": 20.5333337624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ん、待てよ？　今「お疲れ様」って言ったか？",
      "startTime": 24.9000014464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの打ち上げだよ！",
      "startTime": 30.1333347797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……なるほど、そういうことか\nだからすずに怜、遙子さんもいるんだな",
      "startTime": 35.8333340168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、この間の買い物も\n普段の買い出しにしてはやけに量が多かったな",
      "startTime": 41.5000006835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、言ってなかったっけ？　あはは、ごめんごめん\n買い物が楽しくって、つい言うの忘れてたよ～",
      "startTime": 50.2333370686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "さーさー、そんなことより座って座って\n早速今から、芽衣が出しものをしちゃうよ～！",
      "startTime": 58.4333411377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "出しもの……？\nそんな準備もしてたのか",
      "startTime": 64.0333411377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "今回お披露目するのは～……\n怜ちゃん、遙子ちゃん、すずにゃんの物真似だよ！",
      "startTime": 69.9000078043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "まずは～……怜ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 74.033340629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "「う～ん……あと五分だけ……\nあ、マカロン美味しい……」",
      "startTime": 81.9000113647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣……\n怜が凄い顔で睨んでるぞ……",
      "startTime": 87.0000098388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれ～？　寝ぼけてる時のマネだったんだけど\nじゃあ、次は遙子ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 94.6333431721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "「佐伯遙子、十七歳です！」\nどう？　似てたかな！？",
      "startTime": 101.4333431721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\n「十七歳より若い子に言われると辛い」？",
      "startTime": 105.2666765054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、最後はすずにゃん！\n「私こそが、二代目星降る奇跡――成宮すずですわ！」",
      "startTime": 113.6666765054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "一応噛まないバージョンにしたんだけど、どう？\n……え、「似てるけど、その気遣いがかえって辛い」？",
      "startTime": 126.400014925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう、{user}さん！？\nなんか変な空気になっちゃったよ～！",
      "startTime": 134.4435393129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "似てる、似てないの前に、内容がな",
      "startTime": 137.733339103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（だが、みんな本当にいい笑顔だな）",
      "startTime": 141.7000210285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（同じ大会に出て、ぶつかり合って、成長して……）\n（四人とも、本当にいい経験が出来たみたいだ）",
      "startTime": 149.9000210285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ジャケット撮影当日",
      "startTime": 153.671744585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "うひゃ～！　猫ちゃんとワンちゃんが一杯だー！\nよ～し！　みんなこっちおいで～！",
      "startTime": 161.3333696206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "お、すずにゃんはワンちゃんが好きなんだ？",
      "startTime": 165.7667019367,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6499.964729999988,
          "startTime": 172.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はね～、この子のお腹に～……まふっ\nすんすん……すーはー……すんすん……すーはー",
      "startTime": 175.5667039712,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7333.296028799992,
          "startTime": 182.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "あれ～？　すずにゃん、どうしたの？\nワンちゃんの甘噛みが痛い？",
      "startTime": 188.8666958332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、それだけ好かれてるってことだよ～\nすずにゃんは可愛いな～、うりうり！",
      "startTime": 195.6666917642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 6299.974902400009,
          "startTime": 197.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（やれやれ……）\n（芽衣とすずが一緒にいると見ていて飽きないな）",
      "startTime": 201.6333502929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、怒んないでよ～、ごろにゃーん\nえへへ、すずにゃんといるとほんと楽しいなー",
      "startTime": 210.9666826089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は猫ちゃんみたい？　あはは、そうかも\nすずにゃんも、ワンちゃんっぽいとこあるよね",
      "startTime": 221.6333472411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
